FBIS4-17856 "drsov082_a_94018" FBIS-SOV-94-082 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Churkin To Remain Envoy `For Immediate Future' Churkin To Remain Envoy `For Immediate Future' LD2804130194 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 1100 GMT 28 Apr 94 LD2804130194 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] Russian Deputy Foreign Minister Vitaliy Churkin will, for the immediate future, remain the president's special envoy to ex-Yugoslavia. This was confirmed today by an official spokesman of the Russian Foreign Ministry.
